query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 b q1 s t1 tq1 u1) NoHashJoin(a1 b q1 s t1 tq1 u1 acc) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 10 AND q1.view_count <= 1000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('blob',
'byte',
'cocoa-touch',
'debugging',
'django-templates',
'escaping',
'jboss',
'linq-to-sql',
'microsoft-excel-2010',
'modal-dialog',
'phantomjs',
'query-optimization',
'unity3d')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow',
'superuser')
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.name IN ('Benefactor',
'Civic Duty',
'Cleanup',
'Documentation User',
'Electorate',
'Explainer',
'Great Answer',
'Inquisitive',
'Promoter',
'Quorum',
'Stellar Question',
'Tag Editor',
'Tenacious',
'Unsung Hero',
'Vox Populi')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 1
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
